Text

If you want to add a text to your schematic, use the
Text menuitem. Then a Dialog will appear where you
can type your text.
If you want to change an existing text, doubleclick
on it and there appear a dialog box so you can change
the text.

You can drag this component to another position
by clicking inside the body of the port, hold
the mouse button, move to the new position,
and release the mouse button.

